results.name: Denominator of n * Product_{d|n} (1 + 1/d).
link: Amiram Eldar, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
maple: with(numtheory): f := proc(n) local i,j; j := n; for i in divisors(n) do j := j*(1+1/i); od; end;
